<P CLASS="western" STYLE="text-indent: 0in;"><FONT COLOR="#000000">
<FONT FACE="OpenSans seriff"><FONT SIZE=5 STYLE="font-size: 16pt"><B>Report a Spam Message</B></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<br />

<P CLASS="western" STYLE="text-indent: 0in;  "><FONT COLOR="#000000">
<FONT FACE=""><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt">
1. Make sure app is enabled in settings.
<br><br>
2. Navigate to SpamResponse app to accept T&amp;Cs.
<br><br>
3. Navigate to your messaging application and select the message you want to report as spam 
by long pressing on the message and selecting "More..".
<br><br>
4. Click on "Report Messages" in the tool-bar.
<br><br>
5. Send the spam report to SpamResponse by selecting "Done."
</FONT></FONT></P>
<br><br>
<P CLASS="western" STYLE="text-indent: 0in;"><FONT COLOR="#000000">
<FONT FACE=""><FONT SIZE=5 STYLE="font-size: 16pt"><B>Report All Messages as Spam</B></FONT></FONT></FONT></P>
<br>
<P CLASS="western" STYLE="text-indent: 0in;  "><FONT COLOR="#000000">
<FONT FACE="OpenSans seriff"><FONT SIZE=3 STYLE="font-size: 11pt">1. Navigate to your messaging application and select the option to 
"Report All Messages" under the list of messages for a particular sender.
<br><br>
2. Send the spam report to SpamResponse by selecting "Done."
</FONT></FONT></P>